text: The Secret of Us Tour is the ongoing fourth concert tour by American singer- songwriter Gracie Abrams, in support of her second studio album, The Secret of Us (2024). The tour began on September 5, 2024, in Portland, United States. It will end on August 27, 2025, in Mexico City, Mexico. ==References== Secret of Us Tour, The Category:Concert tours
title: The Secret of Us Tour
